lead_paragraph: Second-seeded Kirsten Flipkens of Belgium scraped into her sixth quarterfinals of the year at the Tashkent Open, edging Maria Sakkari of Greece 7-6 (0), 3-6, 7-6 (4) on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Flipkens, Tsurenko Reach Tashkent Open Quarterfinals
